# API Token

<% if @current_user != @showing_user %>
This token belongs to ai_agent [<%= raw @showing_user.display_name %>](<%= @showing_user.path %>), but you are able to view it because you are the owner of this ai_agent.

<% end %>
<% if @token.plaintext_token.present? %>
**IMPORTANT: Save this token now - you will not be able to see it again.**

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Name | <%= raw @token.name || 'Unnamed' %> |
| Token | `<%= @token.plaintext_token %>` |
| Created | <%= time_ago_in_words(@token.created_at) %> ago |
| Last Used | <%= @token.last_used_at ? time_ago_in_words(@token.last_used_at) + ' ago' : 'Never' %> |
| Expires | in <%= time_ago_in_words(@token.expires_at) %> |
| Active | <%= @token.active? ? 'Yes' : 'No' %> |
<% else %>
| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Name | <%= raw @token.name || 'Unnamed' %> |
| Token | `<%= @token.obfuscated_token %>` |
| Created | <%= time_ago_in_words(@token.created_at) %> ago |
| Last Used | <%= @token.last_used_at ? time_ago_in_words(@token.last_used_at) + ' ago' : 'Never' %> |
| Expires | in <%= time_ago_in_words(@token.expires_at) %> |
| Active | <%= @token.active? ? 'Yes' : 'No' %> |
<% end %>

